  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WHAT IS MADNESS?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.poster.avif?t=1738043320\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.webm?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.mp4?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Madness Inside\" is a psychological horror walking simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Average time to complete the game: 60-80 minutes</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>There are two endings </u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lieutenant Vic Voyt, chasing a dangerous criminal, unexpectedly finds himself in this dark place where horrifying experiments once took place. Players will explore dark corridors, solve puzzles, and gather clues to uncover the hospital's secrets and find a way out. As they progress, reality blends with nightmares, creating a tense atmosphere of psychological horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.poster.avif?t=1738043320\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.webm?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.mp4?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WARNING: Some people may experience seizures triggered by flashing lights and flickering images, even if they have never been diagnosed with epilepsy. The game contains scenes of violence and murder that may negatively impact mental health. Some elements may not be suitable for certain age groups. It is recommended to responsibly restrict the game's audience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full immersion is recommended using headphones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.poster.avif?t=1738043320\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.webm?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102000/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.mp4?t=1738043320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Genre: Walking simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built on Unreal Engine 5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden notes and references</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an abandoned psychiatric hospital</p>",
